story.title: Chicago Teachers Union March - 5/23/12
story.description: The Chicago Teachers Union held a rally and march on May 23, 2012. I have included my tweets and photos along with a small subset of tweets and pictures from others. Search hashtag #cturally or @ctulocal1 on Twitter, Flickr, etc for much more coverage of the event.
